{"tid":1630863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑踩油驅車撞人　62歲躁爆司機涉瘋駕被捕","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:11:14.000Z","uid":68738,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7772220821b5596ed5dc5da1ebce28b680b55f04","tid":1630863,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191006/photo/bkn-20191006195544626-1006_00822_001_01p.jpg?20191006203305\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191006%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191006195544626-1006_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20191006203305&h=a2a3d233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大埔昨日(5日)有人疑蓄意「踩油」驅車撞人，警方經調查後，今日(6日)上午在區內拘捕一名姓張(62歲)本地男子，涉嫌瘋狂駕駛。他已獲准保釋候查，須於11月上旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n事發於昨午約2時，一名姓李(29歲)私家車男司機，搭載一名姓錢(30歲)男友人前往大埔運頭塘邨，駛至南運路近廣福道交界時，鄰線另一輛私家車懷疑突然切線，兩車險告相撞，雙方隔着車窗對罵後，各自駕車離開。李其後駛抵運頭塘邨巴士總站，再遇對方私家車爆發衝突。有人懷疑遭人跟蹤，「扯火」取出懷疑棍棒及利刀揮舞，更突然把私家車倒後再「踩油」加速，適時站在車頭位置的錢被撞倒捲入車底，身體多處受傷，涉事司機撞人後不顧而去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191006/mobile/bkn-20191006195544626-1006_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191006%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191006195544626-1006_00822_001.html&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6priIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=a6c3d682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191006/mobile/bkn-20191006195544626-1006_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6946f4f89228086c569f8f561bb7a376596e7a4b","tid":1630863,"uid":73281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"Dllm直頭蓄意謀殺"},{"pid":"cba1e5d63e346b52b29d21adc2e8bbeacf7c2afe","tid":1630863,"uid":36441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"香港啲廢老呢幾年真係越黎越囂張 持老賣老好嚴重"},{"pid":"d5bdfb0ee0f9dd63f0adb8700f7899d0a58abefd","tid":1630863,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"意圖殺人下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb6bcbb29131af7423bdf3058cf2c834741ecd9","tid":1630863,"uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:01:45.000Z","msg":"阿蛇阿蛇，我撐你哋架！<br />\n<br />\nOK，朋友。聽日走得喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac4a93c3b82e4da6f7571546dc8732175051793","tid":1630863,"uid":11818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:02:42.000Z","msg":"Mon住睇佢會唔會低調效人"},{"pid":"e3ccff73242e95243886fac519256d0e51f3381c","tid":1630863,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"咩事? 私事定公事?"},{"pid":"4914151527af3e63e85b015c7cd22470791b78c7","tid":1630863,"uid":290639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}